reviewText: I enjoyed this movie sooooooooooooooooooooooooooooo much.  It made me very happy.  Oh yeah, I am also the director, so this review is probably a little biased.
Such a good movie! Hilarious, Ian Karmel seems to be the next big thing in the entertainment industry. He also does some extreme and unpredictable choreography in this flick!

The movie is awesome, a definite shock to your senses but Ian karmel is incredibly BRILLIANT and is on his way to the big time.  He is such a talent.  FUNNY as all get out and steals the show.  Can't wait to see his next fabulous endeavor.  Can I see an OSCAR nod for this young man ???  Go get 'em Ian !!!!
